    <segment id="37">, como</segment>
    <segment id="38">como o procurador-geral de Justi脙搂a (chefe do MP de Goi脙隆s)</segment>
    <segment id="39">, Benedito Torres</segment>
    <segment id="40">, irm脙拢o de Dem脙鲁stenes.</segment>
    <segment id="41">Perillo</segment>
    <segment id="42">脙</segment>
    <segment id="43">漏 investigado pelo Superior Tribunal de Justi脙搂a (STJ)</segment>
    <segment id="44">, Benedito responde a processo no Conselho Nacional do Minist脙漏rio P脙潞blico (CNMP)</segment>
    <segment id="45">, e Dem脙鲁stenes</segment>
    <segment id="46">, depois da cassa脙搂脙拢o no Senado</segment>
    <segment id="47">, 脙漏 alvo de um processo que tramita no Tribunal Regional Federal (TRF) da 1脗陋 Regi脙拢o.</segment>
    <segment id="48">O STJ investiga</segment>
    <segment id="49">comocomo Cachoeira influenciava nomea脙搂脙碌es no governo.</segment>
    <segment id="50">Os di脙隆logos registrados um dia antes da opera脙搂脙拢o d脙拢o detalhes dessa atua脙搂脙拢o.</segment>
    <segment id="51">"</segment>
    <segment id="52">Temos de vencer mais essa batalha a脙颅.</segment>
